      "content": "thanks. i tried the mucinex but it didnt really do much for the pressure. my doctor isnt answering her phone right now and i can barely breathe through my nose. you said sudafed is often safe though... like, is it actually fine to take a standard dose of pseudoephedrine? i dont want to do anything crazy but i'm desperate here.",
